---

Data Source:
The taxonomy data in data/keys_optimized.json is derived from the USDA 
"Keys to Soil Taxonomy (2022 Edition)" by the Natural Resources Conservation Service.
This data is in the public domain and is freely available for educational and
research purposes.

For the original USDA Keys, see:
https://www.nrcs.usda.gov/resources/guides-and-instructions/keys-to-soil-taxonomy

